---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 488
  - Title: Talmud
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Metanoia=Repentance, Renewal and Awakening
---
Great is Teschubah (repentance), for it brings healing to the world.
Great is Teschubah, for it reaches to the Throne of Glory. Great is
Teschubah, for it brings on the Redemption.
